channel.title: Catturato V2 (317 RSPS)
channel.description:
[B][U][CENTER]CATTURATO 317 RSPS [B][U][CENTER]Hey all, I'm here to advertise the release of my RSPS: Catturato 317 RSPS
So you may ask, what makes Catturato different to other Private Servers? Well ... Let me show you [B][U][CENTER]We have many Oldschool Runescape items, such as Full graceful, Ranger's Tunic, Blowpipe. The list goes on.[/CENTER] [B][U][CENTER]See for yourself [IMG]http://imgur.com/Mm2bNIx.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/G3iGfkZ.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/JuecTAD.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/lWJ5LxE.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/FAEX9FD.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/3tQmEAM.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/jrBdSlB.png[/img] [B][U][CENTER] We have a fully working clan management system! [IMG]http://imgur.com/NTYzrbO.png[/img]
[B][U][CENTER]We have all Oldschool Runescape skills (All work! Including Hunter [IMG]http://imgur.com/UX5QNCO.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/mZqXtDE.png[/img]
[B][U][CENTER]We have a fully working Tier/Achievement System! [IMG]http://imgur.com/ogsv7vh.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/igXnpH7.png[/img] [IMG]http://imgur.com/A3c6rhE.png[/img]
[B][U][CENTER]We have a Tutorial to help you understand the basics of the game![/COLOR][/CENTER][/U][/B] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/lXJo17q.png[/img] [B][U][CENTER]We have a all 4 Wilderness bosses (+ many more to chose from) [IMG]http://imgur.com/dBgFxqB.png[/img]
[B][U][CENTER]We have three different game modes to chose from (Regular, Legendary & Iron Man) [IMG]http://imgur.com/M0qJVq2.png[/img]
[B][U][CENTER](If you chose Legendary, you get a special whip that is slightly worse then a regular whip)[/COLOR][/CENTER][/U][/B] [IMG]http://imgur.com/Dh4zpJV.png[/img] [B][U][CENTER]We have a friendly quest tab interface with all the information you need to know about your account![/COLOR][/CENTER][/U][/B] [IMG]http://imgur.com/VK3hD1A.png[/img]
[CENTER][U][B]We have OsBuddy overlays with working Exp Bar [IMG]http://imgur.com/PaAowes.png[/img]
[B][SIZE=4]Catturato also has many more features, come in and try it all for yourself! We aim to be one of most high quality RuneScape Private Servers out there with our dedicated VPS and Webhost both with DDoS protection!
Come along, join us at catturato-ps.com Try the game for yourself, and bring your friends too!
Regards, Catturato Team.
